                      "name": "step1",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. 先选中需要导出的当前页面（仅导出此页）。",
                      "fontFamily": "SF Pro Text",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "RFdZk",
                      "name": "step2",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "2. 点击顶部“导出”并选择 PNG 格式。",
                      "fontFamily": "SF Pro Text",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "4nZLg",
                      "name": "step3",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "3. 确认“单页导出”，即可生成当前页图片。",
                      "fontFamily": "SF Pro Text",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "JQ5JV",
              "name": "区块B-批量导出",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 14,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "19VxM",
                  "name": "t1",
                  "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                  "content": "批量导出与命名建议",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Z6fsZ",
                  "name": "t2",
                  "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "1. 先统一页面尺寸与导出倍率：同一批次尽量保持一致的 Frame 尺寸与 1x/2x 设置，避免后续混用。\n2. 用稳定命名模板：建议“项目_模块_页面_状态_v版本”，例如“StoryApp_Home_Feed_Default_v03”。\n3. 加序号保顺序：多图连续导出时在文件名前加 01/02/03，便于脚本读取与交付对齐。\n4. 导出前做一次快速清理：隐藏草稿层、检查边界留白与文本溢出，减少返工。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "cOoXK",
                  "name": "t3",
                  "fill": "#717171",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "命名尽量避免空格与中文符号，推荐使用下划线或短横线，跨平台更稳定。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "muxcp",
              "name": "区块C-当前会话",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 14,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "x1s2X",
                  "name": "t1",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "content": "直接导出（当前页面）",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "NCR2m",
                  "name": "t2",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "1. 先在画布选中你要导出的页面 Frame。\n2. 在右侧或工具菜单选择 Export / 导出。\n3. 格式选 PNG（需要高清可选 2x）。\n4. 点击导出并保存到本地目录。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "MPn5c",
                  "name": "t3",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "如果你在这个设计环境里批量导出多个页面，通常做法是多选顶层 Frame 后一起导出。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
