              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "500"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "aPXAa",
          "name": "row",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "gap": 12,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "h5a5m",
              "name": "区块A-原理",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": 14,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "GS6HB",
                  "name": "t1",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "区块A｜BokehBG 原理",
                  "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-md",
                  "fontWeight": "600"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "PAdK6",
                  "name": "t2",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "核心结构：底色层 + 光斑层 + 轻遮罩层。光斑层通常由多枚圆形/椭圆形色块组成。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "0QcEf",
                  "name": "t3",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "为什么用多层绝对定位：每个光斑可独立控制位置、尺寸、透明度与颜色，改动互不干扰，复用到不同容器也更稳定。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Iv7oy",
                  "name": "t4",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "为什么用大半径模糊：把硬边色块扩散成柔光，叠色过渡更自然，层次更深，不会出现生硬边缘。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "wfUdU",
                  "name": "t5",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "结论：多层绝对定位负责“可控”，大半径模糊负责“质感”，两者组合是 BokehBG 的关键。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "PingFang SC",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "BT0CD",
              "name": "区块B-调参",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 14,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "KSJ9C",
                  "name": "title",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "区块B｜调参建议与失真排查",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-md",
                  "fontWeight": "600"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "yYnAS",
                  "name": "intro",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "建议按顺序调：先 blur，再 alpha，再位置，最后层级。每次只改一项，便于定位问题。",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "LLfSr",
                  "name": "sec1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--grey-bg",
                  "cornerRadius": "$--radius-sm",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    10,
                    12
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "2oXsj",
                      "name": "sec1t",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "调参建议（简版）",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "zLKtH",
                      "name": "sec1b",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. blur：从小到大加，先找边缘刚变柔的点，避免一上来糊成片。\n2. alpha：主体 0.75-1.00，背景 0.20-0.55，先保主体对比。\n3. 位置：亮斑尽量避开五官/文字中心，优先放在边角与空区。\n4. 层级：主体上方少放高亮虚化层，前景高光要少且弱，防止抢戏。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.45,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "0dOFR",
                  "name": "sec2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--color-warning-bg",
                  "cornerRadius": "$--radius-sm",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    10,
                    12
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "6umlN",
                      "name": "sec2t",
                      "fill": "$--off-black",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "常见失真排查",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "6RuOf",
                      "name": "sec2b",
                      "fill": "$--off-black",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. 发灰发脏：alpha 叠太多或层级混乱；先关上层特效逐层恢复。\n2. 边缘脏圈：blur 过大且贴边；减 blur 或把元素移出主体边缘。\n3. 颜色漂移：多层混色导致偏色；降低彩色层透明度，保留一层主色。\n4. 文字不清：高亮/噪点压住文字；文字区上方清层，提升文字与底色对比。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.45,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$--font-size-sm",
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "I022c",
                  "name": "foot",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "排查原则：先关特效看原图，再按『层级→位置→alpha→blur』顺序回调。",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": "$--font-size-xs",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "hiANT",
              "name": "区块C-代码",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 12,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": 14,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "tU9sh",
                  "name": "c1",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "content": "可直接复制到 VS Code 的实现",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "QdgWO",
                  "name": "c2",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "React 结构（BokehBG.tsx）：\n<div className=\"bokeh-bg\">\n  <span className=\"blob g1\" />\n  <span className=\"blob g2\" />\n  <span className=\"blob g3\" />\n  <span className=\"blob g4\" />\n  <span className=\"blob g5\" />\n  <span className=\"blob g6\" />\n</div>",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "85eGk",
                  "name": "c3",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "CSS 核心（BokehBG.css）：\n.bokeh-bg{position:relative;width:393px;height:852px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff;}\n.blob{position:absolute;border-radius:999px;filter:blur(150px);}\n.g1{left:-35px;top:-49px;width:140px;height:140px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#46F08080 0%,#46F08A15 100%);}\n.g2{left:30px;top:170px;width:160px;height:160px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#7C5CFC60 0%,#7C5CFC20 100%);}\n.g3{left:284px;top:192px;width:140px;height:140px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#7C5CFC50 0%,#7C5CFC10 100%);}\n.g4{left:254px;top:290px;width:200px;height:200px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#EDF04670 0%,#F0E94615 100%);}\n.g5{left:-80px;top:498px;width:180px;height:180px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#46BDF070 0%,#46B3F015 100%);}\n.g6{left:200px;top:736px;width:120px;height:120px;filter:blur(130px);background:linear-gradient(180deg,#F0B64670 0%,#F0CB4615 100%);}",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "PdHrM",
                  "name": "c4",
                  "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "建议：先按原值抄一版，再只改一个参数观察效果，优先调 alpha 和位置，最后再动 blur 半径。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.45,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
